Edition:
Quote: .. heavy fog hung low on the tops. It was 'a day for the king.'
Notes:

Date: 0/0/1951
Source: NZ High Country
Author: MCLEOD
Vol / Page: 43
Edition:
Quote: When you wake up in the morning in a mustering hut and hear the rain beating on the roof someone is sure to poke his head out of the door and look around and say: "It's a day for the King boys!"
